values:
well. summer is here, boiling, and we have no pool. but, i got my speaking task out of the way, i thought i was gonna bomb it. i was taht scared. but i apparently did really well. *shrug* why does that always happen? perhaps ill do the same thing on the chem reigents? think im gonna bomb and get a 95 *derrisive snort* not even in my wildest dreams

~*~*~*

SUMMER IS FINALLY HERE!!!!!! 

mother fucking 85 degrees, christ.

*sigh* havent been here in a while *clears cobwebs* i think its cause i got a myspace, and... yeah. sooo whats been happening? amedee and i are no longer friends cuz of this stupid thing. dana and i are now best friends (^_^), saundra wont admit that shes inlove with ben, and im now jeffs bitch. kinda boring, but hey, this is nny...
gahhh  its raining. BLOODY WEATHER! my uncle made his famous sketi, yum yum. its making me frenzied

well, apparently saundra has been spreading shit about me at "only faggots allowed"... i mean, i TRUSTED her with personal things, and what does she do??? she  tells ppl i dont even know about my personal life. like, she tells heathers cuzins girlfriend stuff ABOUT ME and then she goes and tells heathers cuzin, who inturn tells heather, and it comes back to me. WHAT THE FUCK??? 

also, she told keri that amedee is *hers* and the rest of us should back off.   ok, once again, WHAT THE FUCK??? she has NO RIGHT to tell anyone that. he doesnt even like her as a person, let alone a girlfriend. and, i have her beat to boot about the liking amedee thing. ok, she SO doesnt beat us (dana and i)... saundra has liked him for what? 3 weeks. dana has liked him for 6 months, and i liked him for 2 years. sorry saundra, get better math skills.

no idea what to get the monkey man for his birthday... i have no money, nothing to make him... mom sugguested cookies, that could work. but i feel kinda bad that i cant get him anything nice.... i totally wish i had a job...

dana and i found out yesterday that neither one of us can actually count, and we both should stop the drugs (HA!) immediately.

sick of the cold. 
sick of school.
sick of....

im back! no more groundation! tho i am bored... 


Blue Eyes was being the biggest dick wad today. couldnt even stand it. stupid head. ah well... my food arrives....
GRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR grounded from the net etc for a MONTH a MONTH, GAHHH. STUPID OVER REACTING FATHER!!!! tho, right now im at amedees house. bc amedee rocks my world.

i feel so icky. uncle dicky is here doin laundry so i cant take a shower. so im still in my jammies :). got a new pair of jeans today, v cute. LUFF them. oh god, mom and uncle d are fighting about the super bowl *rolls eyes*

ok, so i thought having an online ournal would be cool... but the thing is, is that nothing ever happens to me... like, in northern ny in the winter, what am i gonna say happened? "oh, and today i went sledding and froze my ass off"? seriously...

k, i went and saw the phantom of the opera last nite, and oooomg it was SOOOO AWSOME!! i went and got the sound track today, and i love that too! the phaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaantom of the opera is there... inside my mind. god i love that song. and the music of the night... and umm all of them. lol, totally nuts i am. k, well not much else to say sooo im not gonna say it, obviously.
WHY, WHY, WHY WONT THEY LET ME GROW UP????? IM ALMOST 16, NOT 6!!!!! GAHHHH!

nothing really happens around here... well, not to me atleast. i talked to dan today, and i was very happy. ummm, i went to wal*mart yesterday... and i saw mr thompson!!! and i was like "HI MR T!!!" and he just kept walkin... and it saddened me, but luckaly, im over it :-D. math reigents wasnt as hard as i thought it was gonna be. ok, the last problem was HARD, and i cant do the logic, but other than that, i think i got it (but dont quote me on that :-p)

k, today was like, the best day ive had in a while! project challenge was totally great (tho i could have smacked this one girl, tab and amanda know who i mean...) the spaghetti thing was totally cool, tho it was really cold. i cannot believe today went so well, i didnt fight with ANYONE!

and the #1 best part of today .:drumroll:.; i learned how to tie a knot in spaghetti *with my tongue*!!!! it was SOOOO cool! w00t w00t, go me!

well, actually, today was a good day. cassie made herself look like an eskimo, it was great. i almost pissed myself laughing at her. saundra isnt coming back, tho she wants to. i told her what i said in here yesterday, and she was all "thanks, nice to see who my true friends are"... but its true. if she cant handle the truth, well, too bad. i cannot even believe it; my uncle is watching harry potter on the disney channel. like he couldnt just go upstairs and get the tape! whaaa. 

u know, if fredie murcury wouldnt have been a gay man... and dead, he would totally be my god :D

great, so now im sick. just dandy. and saundra might be coming back. tho, idk if its true, i heard it from keri. but if she does come back, i may move away. idt i can handle her on a day to day basis anymore. im just so used to not fighting that im not shure i could do it now.... had an assembly for boces today, and im gonna go look at the allied health program, and the intro to health occupations. i wanted to see the unique occupations thing, but they didnt have a peeky thing into that. i really would like to go into microbiology (possibly marinemicrobiology)... and i think my fall back will be pharmacy. 

no idea why everyone thinks they have to fight with me... im gettin rather sick of it... infact, its really pissing me off. i think ill go listen to some loud music to piss my dad off...

well, its official. i like someone other than amedee (and if you didnt know that, you should be *thumped* very hard by amanda)... im so very proud of my self :-D. hahaha, yesterday i wrote a note to... keri i think and i was saying how cool my "pen is" and i looked at it again, and it looked like "penis" bc my handwriting was all smooshed together. i snorted trying not to laugh, and putney gave me a dirty look, but idc, it was funny. i need serious help dont i? ah well...

krystal was at school today. which was cool. we all love her :-D.

mrs walsh was a nazi in chorus again today, and i was singing soprano again by mistake. i swear, i cant take anymore soulfech, or how ever you spell it. 

way excited for saturday.... :)

nothing good happened today... but on the bright side, nothing bad happened... i got a 95 on the essay we had to write for To Kill a Mockingbird, that was kinda cool i guess. i took amedees hoodie again, as i know how much it pisses my mom off (and it smells REALLY good, like uber good of doom good)... amanda sugguested that i pry up a floor board and put my BoS in the space, but idt that would work. i could try it i suppose. perhaps later....

linkin park is SO FRICKIN AWSOME!!!!

i am having the worst 2005 ever (well, i know there hasnt been another one, but that isnt the point) this whole year so far has sucked major ass. my book of shaddows has "mysteriously" disappeared (ie: i think my mom took it) so i now have no where to vent untill i buy another notbook. also, i messed things up really really badly between amedee and tab... and i feel horrible about it. i didnt intentionally do it. i know how much they mean to each other, and i would never want to sabotage that. i used to want to over the summer, but... things are different now. cassaundra wasnt very sympthetic...

lets see if i have anything happy to talk about... *thinks*.... well, atleast i know i am a self centered drama queen. hip hip horray for me :-/

*sigh* well, this is my journal. it prolly wont be that interesting, as im a boring person anyways. but if you somehow find the entries to follow miraculusly holding you attention, by all means, keep reading :-d... well, as i have dial up i prolly should be going, as my parents will prolly flip if im on too long...
